.TH LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-OUT-MST-VARIANCE 1
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-out-msat-variance \- variance of outbound forwarded amounts
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning node-listforwards-out-msat-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the variance of outbound millisatoshi amounts across forwarded payments.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key out_msat_variance.
